Sanity Build Automation
=======================

Automate the running of your rspec, cucumber, Test::Unit tests tests, integration and Javascript tests and other rake tasks on every branch and every commit of your project.

Features:

* Multiple project support [done]
* Live Commandline output [done]
* Web management tool and build status information [started]
* Exclude branches you don't want to build [done]
* Builds every commit since last build or the last one (when Sanity first starts) [done]

Running
-------
Server:
    script/build_server

Web interface:
    script/server

